1.
Go to FANN-2.2.0-Source/VS2010
Run fann MVS solutinon file in MVS13 
Choose BUILD -> Batch build, select all and press rebuild.

2.
Project->Properties

C/C++ -> Additional Include Directories-> FANN-2.2.0-Source\src\include
	
Linker->General-> Additional Library Directories-> FANN-2.2.0-Source\bin

Linker->Input-> Additional Dependencies->      fanndouble.lib
	                                       or
	                                       fannfloat.lib

Copy all .dll files from FANN-2.2.0-Source\bin to your project

3.
Try run included examples to see if it works.
